1. Install Python 3
   https://www.python.org/downloads/

2. Install PySide 
   http://qt-project.org/wiki/Get-PySide

3. Execute "start.py" in this folder with Python 3.
   e.g. python3 start.py
   
On the first start a sub folder "Imperialism Remake User Data"
in the current user home folder is created. It contains
preferences and logs.

Website: http://remake.twelvepm.de/
Troubleshooting: http://remake.twelvepm.de/home/contact/